1
00:00:02,869 --> 00:00:04,530
在我漫长的生命当中
ELlJAH: Over the course
of my long life...

2
00:00:05,105 --> 00:00:08,404
我逐渐相信
我们的命运与血亲相连
...I have come to believe that we are bound
forever to those with whom we share blood.

3
00:00:09,509 --> 00:00:11,409
我们虽无法选择家人
And while we may not choose our family...

4
00:00:12,178 --> 00:00:13,941
这份血缘却是我们最强大的力量
...that bond can be
our greatest strength...

5
00:00:14,814 --> 00:00:16,714
抑或是最深切的遗憾
...or our deepest regret.

6
00:00:17,951 --> 00:00:21,011
从我有记忆以来
就一直陷于这不幸的循环中
This unfortunate truth has haunted me
for as long as I can recall.

7
00:00:21,354 --> 00:00:25,290
（三百年前 密西西比河）

8
00:00:26,292 --> 00:00:27,816
你怎么看？
What do you make of that?

9
00:00:28,928 --> 00:00:30,190
没有标志，没有旗帜
No banner, no flag.

10
00:00:30,630 --> 00:00:32,154
凭空出现
Floated in out of nowhere.

11
00:00:32,766 --> 00:00:33,960
谜之船
A miracle ship.

12
00:00:35,702 --> 00:00:37,294
为什么会一直停在那里？
Why is it just sitting out there?

13
00:00:39,339 --> 00:00:41,000
不如我们去看看吧
I suppose we ought to find out.

14
00:00:54,454 --> 00:00:56,183
人都去哪了？
Where in hell is everyone?

15
00:00:57,057 --> 00:00:58,217
一艘废弃的船
Deserted.

16
00:00:58,725 --> 00:01:00,590
所以船上的东西见者有份
Which makes everything
in the hold legally forfeit.

17
00:01:00,760 --> 00:01:02,057
大家自己拿吧
Take what suits you.

18
00:01:04,297 --> 00:01:05,764
这个你又怎么看？
What do you make that?

19
00:01:11,037 --> 00:01:12,095
打开它
Open it up.

20
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,845
什么鬼东西？
What the hell?

21
00:01:40,733 --> 00:01:41,927
你好
REBEKAH: Hello.

22
00:01:46,739 --> 00:01:48,570
长途旅行之后见到这么一张帅脸
Lovely to see
such a handsome face

23
00:01:48,741 --> 00:01:50,072
真是开心
after a long journey.

24
00:01:50,243 --> 00:01:51,505
我能吃他吗，哥哥？
Can I eat him, brother?

25
00:01:51,845 --> 00:01:53,472
我建议你别这么做
ELlJAH: I'd rather you didn't.

26
00:01:56,983 --> 00:01:58,473
不用害怕
There's no need to be afraid.

27
00:01:59,219 --> 00:02:00,880
照我说的做
You'll do exactly as I say.

28
00:02:01,855 --> 00:02:03,117
你不会记得这一切
You'll remember nothing.

29
00:02:04,457 --> 00:02:05,822
我不会记得这一切
I will remember nothing.

30
00:02:06,292 --> 00:02:07,554
我们航行了好久
We have had a very
long journey,

31
00:02:07,727 --> 00:02:08,819
途中，我们很不幸地
wherein which,
unfortunately,

32
00:02:08,995 --> 00:02:09,984
失去了全部船员
we lost all of our crew.

33
00:02:10,163 --> 00:02:12,358
因此，我们请求你帮个忙
Therefore, I would ask you
to kindly transport

34
00:02:12,532 --> 00:02:14,056
把我们的东西运到岸上去
our belongings
to the shore.

35
00:02:14,534 --> 00:02:16,525
你们究竟是什么怪物？
What kind
of hell demons are you?

36
00:02:16,703 --> 00:02:18,034
我们是吸血鬼，亲爱的
REBEKAH: We're vampires, darling.

37
00:02:18,905 --> 00:02:20,133
吸血鬼真祖
The Original vampires.

38
00:02:21,541 --> 00:02:23,441
蕾贝卡，以利亚
Rebekah, Elijah.

39
00:02:23,943 --> 00:02:26,411
我们的兄弟柯尔跟芬恩
愿他们安息
Our brothers, Kol and Finn,
may they rest in peace.

40
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:28,939
是要让我压轴出场吗？
KLAUS: Are we saving
the best for last?

41
00:02:29,382 --> 00:02:31,111
我们同母异父的兄弟尼克劳斯
And our half-brother Niklaus.

42
00:02:33,186 --> 00:02:34,881
别理他，他就是个野兽
Ignore him.
He's a beast.

43
00:02:40,426 --> 00:02:42,860
从欧洲逃离，幸免于海难
We fled Europe and
survived the seas.

44
00:02:43,029 --> 00:02:44,758
你愿意我一踏上新家园的岸边
Would you rather
I arrive hungry

45
00:02:44,931 --> 00:02:46,523
就饥肠辘辘吗？
on the shores
of our new homeland?

46
00:02:46,966 --> 00:02:49,696
尼克劳斯，你的行为总是这么
无与伦比
Niklaus, your manners are,
as always, without equal.

47
00:02:51,137 --> 00:02:53,605
先生，劳烦你告诉我们
Sir, would you be so
good as to tell us

48
00:02:53,773 --> 00:02:55,502
这里是哪里呢？
where it is that
we have landed?

49
00:02:56,409 --> 00:02:58,240
法国殖民地路易斯安那州
The French colony
of Louisiana.

50
00:02:58,912 --> 00:03:01,403
上岸之后的城市叫纽奥良
Off the shores of a town
they've named New Orleans.

51
00:03:01,814 --> 00:03:03,509
非常感谢
Well, thank you so much.

52
00:03:05,251 --> 00:03:07,446
我建议你为自己
Oh, I do recommend
that you find yourself

53
00:03:07,620 --> 00:03:09,247
找个帮手拿行李
further assistance
for the luggage.

54
00:03:09,956 --> 00:03:11,321
奉上我真诚的歉意
My sincere apologies.

55
00:03:28,508 --> 00:03:33,104
片名：创始吸血鬼（第一季）
剧名：直到永远

56
00:03:40,687 --> 00:03:41,949
（卢梭酒吧）

57
00:03:42,155 --> 00:03:44,487
什么风把你吹来快活之都？
主演：约瑟夫摩根
CAMl: So, what brings you
to the Big Easy?

58
00:03:45,158 --> 00:03:46,455
我以前在这住过
I used to live here.

59
00:03:46,826 --> 00:03:48,191
真的吗？什么时候？
Really? When?

60
00:03:48,528 --> 00:03:50,120
感觉像是一百年之前了
Oh, feels like
a hundred years ago.

61
00:03:50,296 --> 00:03:51,763
我刚一个人搬到这里
主演：丹尼尔吉利斯
I just moved here myself.

62
00:03:51,798 --> 00:03:52,787
你为什么回来？
主演：丹尼尔吉利斯
What brought you back?

63
00:03:52,966 --> 00:03:54,331
我的弟弟在这里
Well, my brother
is here somewhere.

64
00:03:54,534 --> 00:03:57,025
恐怕他已经给自己惹了一点麻烦
主演：克莱儿荷特
I'm afraid he might have gotten himself
into a bit of a bind.

65
00:03:57,437 --> 00:03:59,234
你这语气似乎司空见惯了
主演：菲比托金
You say that like it's
a common occurrence.

66
00:03:59,405 --> 00:04:00,736
他这人很复杂
Well, he's complicated...

67
00:04:02,275 --> 00:04:03,242
目中无人…
Defiant. 

68
00:04:03,276 --> 00:04:06,404
粗野无礼、还有点喜怒无常
主演：查尔斯麦可戴维斯
Ill-mannered.
And a little temperamental.

69
00:04:09,816 --> 00:04:11,408
我们不是同个父亲生的
See, we don't share
the same father.

70
00:04:11,584 --> 00:04:12,676
当然了，我不在意这些
Of course,
that never bothered me,

71
00:04:12,852 --> 00:04:14,979
但我弟弟却对此怨恨不已
but my brother
resents it deeply.

72
00:04:15,154 --> 00:04:16,815
从来没找到归属感
Never felt
like he belonged.

73
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:20,625
总之，他总是容易惹上麻烦
主演：丹妮耶拉皮纳达
All told, he has
a long history
of getting himself
into trouble.

74
00:04:20,827 --> 00:04:22,124
我猜你总是帮他
And I'm guessing
you have a long history

75
00:04:22,295 --> 00:04:23,319
解决麻烦
of getting him
out of it.

76
00:04:24,397 --> 00:04:25,921
你弟弟惹上什么麻烦了？
What kind of bind
is your brother in?

77
00:04:26,099 --> 00:04:27,589
他觉得这座城市里有人
主演：莉雅派普斯
He believes there are
people in this town

78
00:04:27,767 --> 00:04:29,166
在密谋对付他
that are conspiring
against him.

79
00:04:29,836 --> 00:04:32,168
自恋加妄想症
主演：丹妮儿坎贝尔
Wow.
Narcissistic and paranoid.

80
00:04:33,740 --> 00:04:36,573
抱歉
我是个有心理学硕士学位的酒保
Sorry. Bartender with a grad degree
in psychology.

81
00:04:36,743 --> 00:04:38,040
职业病
Total cliche.

82
00:04:38,645 --> 00:04:40,135
听我说，卡蜜儿
Listen, Camille.

83
00:04:40,313 --> 00:04:42,747
其实我来这里
是想找个人问一下
I'm looking for someone
who might shed some light

84
00:04:42,915 --> 00:04:44,246
他正面临的困境
on his current
predicament.

85
00:04:44,417 --> 00:04:46,180
她在这里工作，简安德弗罗
She works here.
Jane-Anne Deveraux.

86
00:04:46,352 --> 00:04:47,842
知道她在哪里吗？
Any idea where
I might find her?

87
00:04:48,021 --> 00:04:50,319
不知道，但我知道谁有可能知道
No, but I know
someone who might.

88
00:04:50,990 --> 00:04:52,548
欢迎来到纽奥良
Welcome to New Orleans,

89
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:54,886
新月之城的明珠
in the crown jewel
of the Crescent City,

90
00:04:55,161 --> 00:04:56,389
法语区
the French Quarter.

91
00:04:56,763 --> 00:05:00,062
爵士乐、什锦饭、爱情，还有诗歌
Jazz and jambalaya,
romance and poetry,

92
00:05:00,433 --> 00:05:03,698
更不用说夜幕之下的骚动了
not to mention things
that go bump in the night.

93
00:05:05,004 --> 00:05:07,404
吸食人血的怪物
Monsters that feed
off human blood.

94
00:05:07,907 --> 00:05:09,636
复仇心切的亡魂
Vengeful spirits
of the dead.

95
00:05:10,276 --> 00:05:13,211
还有我最喜欢的女巫
And my personal favorite,
the witches.

96
00:05:13,813 --> 00:05:16,145
这里是巫术店“灰色花园”
制片：兰斯安德森
Here we have the voodoo shop
Jardin Gris.

97
00:05:16,316 --> 00:05:18,307
请进，体验一下巫术吧
Go in,
browse for a hex.

98
00:05:21,421 --> 00:05:23,412
你要一直跟踪我吗，以利亚？
Are you gonna continue
following me, Elijah...

99
00:05:23,790 --> 00:05:24,984
还是你想谈谈？
...or do you want to talk?

100
00:05:25,291 --> 00:05:26,519
你知道我是谁
You know who I am.

101
00:05:26,726 --> 00:05:28,990
老是穿西装的吸血鬼真祖
Original vampire,
always wears a suit.

102
00:05:29,395 --> 00:05:31,590
你们家族在女巫界很出名
You and your family are
famous amongst the witches.

103
00:05:31,998 --> 00:05:33,488
尤其是…
制片：朗恩麦克劳德
Especially with

104
00:05:33,533 --> 00:05:35,296
你弟弟又回来了
your brother back in town.

105
00:05:35,501 --> 00:05:36,900
尼克劳斯来这里是因为他得知
Well, Niklaus is here
because he learned

106
00:05:37,070 --> 00:05:38,799
有个女巫在密谋对付他
that a witch was
conspiring against him,

107
00:05:38,971 --> 00:05:40,905
一个叫做简安德弗罗的人
someone by the name
of Jane-Anne Deveraux.

108
00:05:41,207 --> 00:05:43,198
如果他要找简安，那他晚了一步
Well, if he's looking for Jane-Anne,
he's a little late.

109
00:05:47,213 --> 00:05:48,976
你是说她已经死了？
Are you telling me she's dead?

110
00:05:52,685 --> 00:05:53,481
跟我来
Come on.

111
00:05:53,519 --> 00:05:56,420
她妹妹苏菲会希望跟你谈谈的
编剧：麦克纳度奇，茱莉普烈克
Her sister Sophie is gonna
wanna talk to you.

112
00:05:56,989 --> 00:05:59,219
导演：克里斯葛端斯莫

113
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,617
那就是简安？
That's Jane-Anne?

114
00:06:30,223 --> 00:06:31,850
在大庭广众下被杀让所有人看到
Killed in public
for anyone to find.

115
00:06:32,058 --> 00:06:34,253
来这里的人都是女巫
Only people come 'round here
are the witches.

116
00:06:35,862 --> 00:06:37,591
现在她妹妹来取她的尸体了
Now her sister has come
to take her body.

117
00:06:38,231 --> 00:06:39,630
她的灵魂无法安息
Her spirit can't rest
until it's been

118
00:06:39,799 --> 00:06:41,494
除非得到妥善的安葬
properly interred
in the cemetery.

119
00:06:43,736 --> 00:06:46,705
拜托告诉我我弟弟跟这件事无关
Please tell me that my brother
had nothing to do with this.

120
00:06:46,873 --> 00:06:49,501
无关，简安的死是因为施魔法被发现
No. Jane-Anne died because
she got caught doing magic.

121
00:06:49,942 --> 00:06:51,807
什么叫施魔法被发现？
What do you mean,
she got caught doing magic?

122
00:06:56,449 --> 00:06:58,007
你想知道谁杀了简安吗？
You want to know
who killed Jane-Anne?

123
00:06:58,184 --> 00:07:00,311
你马上就会亲眼见到马赛尔的作为了
You're about to get your first glimpse
of Marcel in action.

124
00:07:00,486 --> 00:07:01,544
吸血鬼马赛尔？
The vampire Marcel?

125
00:07:01,721 --> 00:07:05,054
你们家族离开后发生了一些事
马赛尔也变了
Things have changed since your family
left town, and Marcel has changed.

126
00:07:10,463 --> 00:07:12,397
我求求你快藏起来吧
I'm asking you,
stay hidden.

127
00:07:12,832 --> 00:07:15,528
如果让马赛尔发现一名女巫
把真祖引回来
If Marcel finds out that a witch
lured the Originals back into town,

128
00:07:15,701 --> 00:07:16,998
我的族人会遭到屠杀的
my people will be
slaughtered.

129
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:22,306
瞧瞧，我们发现了什么？
Well, well, well.
What have we here?

130
00:07:23,242 --> 00:07:24,937
我得告诉你，苏菲，这个卫角
I got to tell you, Soph,
this street corner

131
00:07:25,111 --> 00:07:27,909
今晚可不是你们族人的幸运之地
is not proving the luckiest spot
for your family tonight.

132
00:07:31,017 --> 00:07:32,484
不到半小时之前
我们在这给你姊姊
Not half an hour ago,
we had to teach

133
00:07:32,652 --> 00:07:33,914
好好上了一课
your sister
a little lesson.

134
00:07:34,353 --> 00:07:35,843
我们在让她的灵魂安息，马赛尔
We're putting her
to rest, Marcel.

135
00:07:36,389 --> 00:07:37,913
别来打扰我们
Leave us alone.

136
00:07:38,157 --> 00:07:39,590
我可没允许你移动尸体
I never said you
could move the body.

137
00:07:39,959 --> 00:07:42,757
事实上，我是特意把她留在这里的
Matter of fact,
I left her here for a reason.

138
00:07:43,162 --> 00:07:44,629
以做逵
Send a message.

139
00:07:45,064 --> 00:07:48,363
如果任何人想要叛变
If anybody is thinking
of joining some kind of rebellion,

140
00:07:48,534 --> 00:07:52,265
我明确规定过女巫不准在法语区施魔法
my rules state that witches
can't practice magic in the Quarter,

141
00:07:52,472 --> 00:07:54,872
但我仍听到风声说
and yet a little birdie
informed me

142
00:07:55,041 --> 00:07:56,531
简安在偷偷地用魔法
that Jane-Anne
was cooking up

143
00:07:56,709 --> 00:07:58,574
密谋些什么
something magically
delicious.

144
00:07:59,946 --> 00:08:01,174
对了
Oh, yeah,

145
00:08:01,347 --> 00:08:03,440
趁你们都在，我问一下
while I have you,
quick Q and A.

146
00:08:03,616 --> 00:08:06,084
我的老朋友，混合种克劳斯
My old friend,
the hybrid, Klaus,

147
00:08:06,252 --> 00:08:07,981
他突然冒了出来
he just happened to
show up out of the blue.

148
00:08:08,154 --> 00:08:10,884
谁都不找，偏找简安
Asking for, of
all people, Jane-Anne.

149
00:08:11,491 --> 00:08:12,617
有人知道为什么吗？
Any idea why?

150
00:08:13,292 --> 00:08:14,589
我不知道
I don't know.

151
00:08:15,094 --> 00:08:17,221
女巫从不插手吸血鬼的事
Witches don't get involved
in vampire business.

152
00:08:18,531 --> 00:08:20,522
不配合我，你一定会后悔
That would be pretty stupid...

153
00:08:21,100 --> 00:08:22,431
我向你保证
...that's for sure.

154
00:08:23,503 --> 00:08:24,902
忠告你一句
Tell you what.

155
00:08:25,805 --> 00:08:27,397
回你的餐厅去
Go back to the restaurant.

156
00:08:27,573 --> 00:08:29,803
好好煮你那出名的秋葵汤
Cook up some
of that famous gumbo.

157
00:08:29,976 --> 00:08:31,443
伺候好游客吧
Keep those tourists happy.

158
00:08:31,978 --> 00:08:33,707
- 把尸体带走
- 什么？
-Take the body.
-What?!

159
00:08:34,013 --> 00:08:36,379
不，不要，住手，马赛尔
No. Stop. Stop. Marcel!

160
00:08:36,549 --> 00:08:38,312
我先暂时保管你姊姊的尸体
MARCEL: I'm gonna hold on
to your sister's body,

161
00:08:38,484 --> 00:08:40,714
以防你想起来为什么克劳斯会来这里
in case maybe you remember
why Klaus is here.

162
00:08:40,853 --> 00:08:42,445
马赛尔，求求你
SOPHlE: Marcel, please.

163
00:08:42,655 --> 00:08:43,952
她的灵魂会无法安息的
Her body won't be at peace.

164
00:08:44,123 --> 00:08:46,091
那可不关我的事
Not my problem.

165
00:08:49,061 --> 00:08:50,426
你是想告诉我，过了这么多年
You mean to tell me,
after all these years,

166
00:08:50,596 --> 00:08:52,826
- 马赛尔还活得好好的？
- 是的
-Marcel is alive and well?
-Quite.

167
00:08:52,999 --> 00:08:54,694
我们兄弟好像卷进了一场战争
Our brother seems to have
wandered into a war zone,

168
00:08:54,867 --> 00:08:56,300
但我还没能找到他
and I haven't been
able to find him.

169
00:08:56,469 --> 00:08:58,664
马赛尔是克劳斯转变的
