是女巫把他引诱过来的
The witches
have lured him here.

201
00:09:58,297 --> 00:09:59,321
我想知道为什么
I'd like to know why.

202
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:23,281
是你把我牵扯进这一切的，简
You got me into this, Jane.

203
00:10:24,223 --> 00:10:26,657
给我力量去了结这一切
Give me the strength
to finish it.

204
00:10:45,645 --> 00:10:46,942
门可以用的
The doors work,
you know.

205
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,811
你在施魔法吗？
You're doing magic?

206
