seeing as Marcel killed her.

213
00:11:27,987 --> 00:11:29,477
我是以利亚
I'm Elijah.

214
00:11:31,290 --> 00:11:32,621
听说过我吗？
Have you
heard of me?

215
00:11:33,492 --> 00:11:34,823
是的
Yes.

216
00:11:35,995 --> 00:11:36,984
告诉我你家人
So why don't you tell me

217
