have to be invited in.

220
00:12:01,220 --> 00:12:04,087
但既然我已经孤注一掷了
进来吧
But since I'm desperate,
come on in.

221
00:12:06,759 --> 00:12:08,386
我们可以在这自由地说话
We can talk freely here.

222
00:12:09,195 --> 00:12:10,890
那你最好快说
Then I suggest
you start talking.

223
00:12:12,465 --> 00:12:14,262
你姊姊想要尼克劳斯怎样？
What did your sister
want with Niklaus?

224
00:12:15,101 --> 00:12:16,090
还不明显吗？
Isn't it obvious?

225
00:12:16,268 --> 00:12:18,566
我们和吸血鬼之间有问题了
我们需要帮助
We have a vampire problem,
and we need help.

226
00:12:18,971 --> 00:12:21,064
马赛尔有一支部队支援他
Marcel has an army
backing him.

227
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:23,071
女巫们一直想要反击
The witches have been
trying to fight back.

228
00:12:23,242 --> 00:12:24,539
但我们运气不好
We haven't had
much luck

229
00:12:24,710 --> 00:12:26,701
直到我姊姊简安过见了一个女孩
until my sister
Jane-Anne met a girl.

230
00:12:27,513 --> 00:12:29,344
一个路过此地的狼人
Awerewolf passing
through the Quarter

231
