in Virginia.

232
00:12:32,752 --> 00:12:35,380
她和你弟弟有某种特殊的联系
She had a special
connection to your brother.

233
00:12:35,688 --> 00:12:36,848
什么样的联系？
What kind
of connection?

234
00:12:37,056 --> 00:12:40,150
很显然他们共度了一些时光
Apparently, they spent
some time together.

235
00:12:40,326 --> 00:12:41,623
一切就顺理成章地发生了
One thing led
to another,

236
00:12:41,794 --> 00:12:44,228
现在这个特殊的狼人女孩
and now this special
werewolf girl,

237
00:12:44,396 --> 00:12:48,196
她怀孕了，她腹中孩子的父亲
she's pregnant,
and the father
of the child
she's carrying

238
00:12:48,367 --> 00:12:49,834
就是你弟弟克劳斯
is your brother, Klaus.

239
00:12:50,302 --> 00:12:51,667
不可能
It's impossible.

240
00:12:52,204 --> 00:12:53,535
没什么不可能
Nothing is impossible,

241
00:12:53,873 --> 00:12:55,898
尤其是发生在你弟弟身上的事
especially not when it comes
to your brother.

242
00:12:56,375 --> 00:12:57,672
想一想
Think about it.

243
00:12:57,843 --> 00:13:00,277
大家都叫他混合种，对吧？
They call him
the Hybrid, right?

244
00:13:01,781 --> 00:13:03,180
带她出来
Bring her out.

245
00:13:19,265 --> 00:13:20,630
你是谁？
Who the hell are you?

246
00:13:29,742 --> 00:13:31,266
让我们单独说两句话
Give us a moment, please.

247
00:13:34,113 --> 00:13:36,581
她们把你强行关在这里？
So, have they been holding you here
against your will?

248
00:13:37,616 --> 00:13:40,585
她们把我引到河口，抓住了我
They lured me out to the bayou
and grabbed me.

249
00:13:41,353 --> 00:13:44,880
然后施展了这些古怪的巫术
Then they did all these
weird, witchy tests.

250
00:13:45,658 --> 00:13:47,717
我不明白这怎么可能
Not that I understand
how this could happen.

251
00:13:47,893 --> 00:13:50,691
我是说吸血鬼没有生命
I mean,
vampires are dead.

252
00:13:51,397 --> 00:13:52,591
他们不能生育
They can't have children.

253
00:13:52,765 --> 00:13:54,323
也许如果你了解我弟弟的故事
Perhaps if you knew
my brother's story,

254
00:13:54,500 --> 00:13:56,058
