it might explain
how this is possible.

255
00:13:56,335 --> 00:13:57,427
请允许我…
Here.
If I may.

256
00:13:57,603 --> 00:13:59,093
你要干什么？
What are you doing?

257
00:13:59,271 --> 00:14:00,568
别紧张
Relax.

258
00:14:02,575 --> 00:14:04,099
如果你对我敞开心扉
If you open
your mind to me...

259
00:14:04,844 --> 00:14:06,072
我会告诉你
...I can show you.

260
00:14:11,684 --> 00:14:14,448
