In the beginning,
our family was human.

261
00:14:15,421 --> 00:14:17,116
在一千年之前
A thousand years ago now.

262
00:14:17,323 --> 00:14:19,348
快点，亨利，兄弟们又打起来了
Come on, Henry, our brothers
are fighting again.

263
00:14:19,658 --> 00:14:21,853
尽管母亲对黑魔法有所涉猎
ELlJAH: Although our mother
dabbled in the dark arts,

264
00:14:22,027 --> 00:14:23,585
我们充其量只是想要在困难时期
we were largely just a family
trying to survive

265
00:14:23,762 --> 00:14:26,230
试图努力存活下去
at a time when it was quite
difficult to do so.

266
00:14:27,867 --> 00:14:31,462
无论如何
我们过得很开心
And, for better or worse,
we were happy.

267
00:14:32,638 --> 00:14:34,572
然而，直到有天晚上
That is, however,
until one night

268
00:14:34,740 --> 00:14:36,207
我们最小的弟弟被杀了
our youngest brother
was killed

269
00:14:36,375 --> 00:14:38,275
凶手是村子里最大的威胁
