270
00:14:38,677 --> 00:14:39,905
弟弟
Brother!

271
00:14:41,513 --> 00:14:45,108
这些人可以在月圆之时变身为狼
Men that could transform themselves
into wolves during the full moon.

272
00:14:46,151 --> 00:14:47,778
我们的家人伤心欲绝
Our family was devastated.

273
00:14:48,854 --> 00:14:50,719
尼克劳斯尤甚
None more than Niklaus.

274
00:14:51,390 --> 00:14:53,051
父亲决心要保护我们
Desperate to protect
the rest of us,

275
00:14:53,225 --> 00:14:55,090
于是逼迫母亲
our father forced
our mother to call

276
00:14:55,261 --> 00:14:57,821
使用黑魔法，让我们变强
upon her black magic
in order to make us stronger.

277
00:14:58,864 --> 00:14:59,956
喝下去
Drink!

278
00:15:00,966 --> 00:15:02,263
喝
Drink!

279
00:15:03,669 --> 00:15:05,569
就这样，初代吸血鬼诞生
Thus, the first
vampires were born.

280
00:15:06,071 --> 00:15:08,437
但我们拥有的速度、力量
But with this speed,
this strength,

281
00:15:08,607 --> 00:15:12,407
还有不死之身，让我们异常饥饿
this immortality
came a terrible hunger.

282
00:15:13,545 --> 00:15:15,911
尼克劳斯尤甚
No one felt this hunger
more than Niklaus.

283
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:22,617
他第一次杀人之后
When he killed for the first time,

284
00:15:22,788 --> 00:15:24,415
看清了自己的本质
we knew what he truly was.

285
00:15:29,094 --> 00:15:30,356
尼克劳斯
Niklaus!

286
00:15:31,363 --> 00:15:32,990
我这是怎么了？
What is happening to me?

287
00:15:33,198 --> 00:15:35,758
不，别过去
别过去
No, don't! Don't!

288
00:15:36,902 --> 00:15:39,268
父亲，好痛啊
Father! It hurts!

289
00:15:45,110 --> 00:15:47,738
他是个野兽，恶心的怪物
He's a beast.
An abomination.

290
00:15:52,351 --> 00:15:53,978
他不只是个吸血鬼
He wasn't just a vampire.

