00:16:02,027 --> 00:16:04,257
夺人性命之后才会放动
It isn't activated
until you take a life.

294
00:16:04,430 --> 00:16:06,022
尼克劳斯是母亲和别人的私生子
Niklaus was the result
of an indiscretion

295
00:16:06,198 --> 00:16:07,790
她一直瞒着我们
our mother had hidden
from us all.

296
00:16:08,734 --> 00:16:11,567
他的亲生父亲是一个狼人
An affair with
a werewolf like yourself.

297
00:16:12,004 --> 00:16:13,904
父亲对这背叛感到震怒
Infuriated by this betrayal,

298
00:16:14,073 --> 00:16:15,836
要求母亲对克劳斯施咒
my father forced our mother
to cast a spell that would

