Classic me.

313
00:17:02,054 --> 00:17:03,521
我不能帮他找藉口
I cannot excuse his behavior,

314
00:17:03,689 --> 00:17:05,816
不过你要明白
but you must understand

315
00:17:05,991 --> 00:17:07,618
几百年来
that our father hunted him,

316
00:17:07,793 --> 00:17:09,522
父亲一直追杀他
