323
00:17:23,809 --> 00:17:25,538
我以为他会因此快乐
I thought this
would make him happy.

324
00:17:26,812 --> 00:17:28,439
但他比从前更愤怒
He was angrier than ever.

325
00:17:30,082 --> 00:17:32,175
我想，或许这孩子
I wonder if, perhaps,
this baby

326
00:17:32,351 --> 00:17:35,650
可以帮我弟弟找回快乐
might be a way
for my brother to find happiness.

327
00:17:36,822 --> 00:17:38,653
我回他自己
A way to save him from himself.

328
00:17:41,326 --> 00:17:42,725
