I'm glad you feel that way.

329
00:17:43,228 --> 00:17:44,820
因为我们需要你的帮助
Because we need your help.

330
00:17:45,130 --> 00:17:46,791
你到底要什么？
What, precisely,
is it that you want,

331
00:17:46,965 --> 00:17:48,557
这又跟这女孩有什么关系？
