00:28:23,535 --> 00:28:25,526
他甘愿放弃一切
ELlJAH: He's willing
to give up everything.

525
00:28:25,704 --> 00:28:28,332
醒醒吧，以利亚
这有什么好奇怪的呢？
Come on, Elijah.
Does that really surprise you?

526
00:28:28,606 --> 00:28:29,664
我可以看得出
I can already see it.

527
00:28:29,841 --> 00:28:30,967
他正步步得势
He's spiraling.

528
00:28:31,643 --> 00:28:33,008
他肆无忌惮地发泄他的怒火
He's lashing out in blind rage.

529
00:28:33,178 --> 00:28:34,611
上次见他这样发脾气
You know, the last time
I saw him like this

530
00:28:34,779 --> 00:28:36,110
一发就是两百年
it lasted two hundred years.

531
00:28:36,281 --> 00:28:38,647
那就让他耍性子
回来吧
Then leave him to his
temper tantrum and come home.

532
00:28:39,250 --> 00:28:41,309
但愿这场灾难
With any luck,
this misadventure

533
00:28:41,486 --> 00:28:43,852
能带给我们些许清净
will allow us a reprieve
from all of his insanity.

534
00:28:44,289 --> 00:28:45,722
就差一点
He was so close.

535
00:28:45,890 --> 00:28:48,552
当他听到胎儿的心跳
我可以从他的眼中看到
When he heard the baby's heartbeat,
I could see it in his eyes.

536
00:28:48,727 --> 00:28:50,820
他想要这个孩子
He--
He wanted it.

537
00:28:51,830 --> 00:28:54,594
他几乎尝到了幸福的滋味
He could almost taste happiness.

538
00:28:54,766 --> 00:28:56,700
但是他的坏脾气毁了一切
And now his temper
has destroyed it.

539
00:28:58,036 --> 00:28:59,697
即使我能让他恢复理智
Even if I was to return
him to sanity,

540
00:28:59,871 --> 00:29:01,702
他也失去了马赛尔的信任
he just lost Marcel's trust.

541
00:29:02,440 --> 00:29:03,634
看来
So....

542
00:29:03,808 --> 00:29:05,708
我得赶紧去接那个女孩了
I'm almost out
of time to get the girl.

543
00:29:05,977 --> 00:29:07,069
接她？
Get her?

544
00:29:07,278 --> 00:29:08,438
你疯了吗？
Have you lost your mind?

545
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:09,806
我们是开孤儿院的吗？
Are we running an orphanage now?

546
00:29:09,981 --> 00:29:11,243
你怎么说尼克劳斯都行
Say what you will about Niklaus,

547
00:29:11,416 --> 00:29:12,906
但我以自己生命担保
but on my life,

548
00:29:13,084 --> 00:29:14,949
我不会让那个孩子有任何不测
I'm not letting anything happen
to that baby.

549
00:29:16,721 --> 00:29:18,655
你找到他就通知我
You find him,
and then you call me.

550
00:29:18,823 --> 00:29:21,417
别担心，我知道怎么应付克劳斯
Don't worry.
I know how to deal with Klaus.

551
00:29:22,093 --> 00:29:23,355
是这样吗？
ELlJAH: Is that so?

552
00:29:24,462 --> 00:29:25,986
怎么不说清楚点？
Please elaborate.

553
00:29:27,198 --> 00:29:28,688
以利亚米卡森
Elijah Mikaelson.

554
00:29:28,833 --> 00:29:32,234
不用，我来，没事的
No. I got it.
It's all good.

555
00:29:41,179 --> 00:29:43,044
是时候我俩好好聊聊了
It's time we had a little chat.

556
00:29:48,953 --> 00:29:51,012
有什么要说的就快说
Well, if you're gonna talk, talk.

557
00:29:51,322 --> 00:29:52,311
我还有事呢
I got things to do.

558
00:29:52,490 --> 00:29:53,923
瞧你，一百年过去了
Oh, my, you have grown
quite confident

559
00:29:54,092 --> 00:29:55,320
你变得这么有自信了，是不是？
over the last century,
haven't you?

560
00:29:55,493 --> 00:29:57,427
我？是你和你弟弟变狂妄了吧
Me? I'd say it's you
and your brother got cocky,

561
00:29:57,595 --> 00:29:59,187
来我的地盘就像到自己家一样
coming to my town
like you own the place.

562
00:29:59,364 --> 00:30:00,831
这里确实曾是我们的地盘
Well, we did own the place, once.

563
00:30:01,199 --> 00:30:02,632
回想起来，那时我们都过得很开心
We were all quite happy here,
as I recall.

564
00:30:02,801 --> 00:30:04,291
但我们始终控制不了
Although we could never control

565
00:30:04,469 --> 00:30:06,403
法语区那些烦人的女巫
those pesky witches
at the French Quarter.

566
00:30:06,571 --> 00:30:07,902
你怎么做到的？
How do you do it?

567
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:11,174
你弟弟问过我同样的问题
Your brother asked me
the same question.

568
00:30:11,342 --> 00:30:13,401
我也给了他同样的回答：这是我的事
I gave him the same answer:
it's my business.

569
00:30:13,578 --> 00:30:16,945
法语区所有的一切都是我的事
Everything in the Quarter
is my business.

570
00:30:17,749 --> 00:30:19,580
克劳斯非常友善地回到这里
Klaus comes into town
all nice and friendly.

571
00:30:19,751 --> 00:30:21,844
后来开始对我所做的一切嗤之以鼻
Then he starts looking
down his nose at what I done,

572
00:30:22,020 --> 00:30:23,544
就好像一切都是他某幅
Iike it's some cheap knock off

573
00:30:23,721 --> 00:30:24,983
破画的廉价仿冒品
of one of his dumb paintings.

574
00:30:25,156 --> 00:30:26,817
然后他就像个小贱人一样生气了
Then he gets pissed off
like a little bitch

575
00:30:26,991 --> 00:30:28,083
咬了我的一个手下
and bites one of my guys.

576
00:30:28,259 --> 00:30:30,557
对克劳斯这种不良行为我表示歉意
Well, I do apologize for
Klaus' poor behavior.

577
00:30:32,163 --> 00:30:33,391
我想你该知道他咬一下
I assume you know
that that bite

578
00:30:33,565 --> 00:30:35,658
会在几天内让你朋友丧命
will kill your friend
within a matter of days.

579
00:30:37,468 --> 00:30:40,403
当然，尼克劳斯的血能治愈他
Of course,
Niklaus' blood would cure him.

580
00:30:42,140 --> 00:30:42,970
什么？
What?

581
00:30:43,107 --> 00:30:46,702
是的，显然混合种的血
可以治愈狼人的咬伤
Yes. Apparently, the blood of the
Hybrid will cure a werewolf bite.

582
00:30:46,811 --> 00:30:49,746
相当方便容易的东西啊
Quite a handy little thing

583
00:30:50,114 --> 00:30:52,412
特别是在需要谈判筹码的时候
when one needs leverage
in negotiation.

584
00:30:53,685 --> 00:30:55,516
什么谈判？
What kind of negotiations
we talking about?

585
00:30:55,687 --> 00:30:57,177
归还女巫简安的尸体
Return the body of
the witch Jane-Anne,

586
00:30:57,355 --> 00:30:58,583
允许她的族人把她好好安葬
allow her people
to put her to rest.

587
00:30:58,823 --> 00:31:01,053
你怎么关心起女巫来了？
What do you care
about the witches?

588
00:31:03,094 --> 00:31:05,221
这就是我的事了，不是吗？
Well, that's my business now,
isn't it?

589
00:31:13,404 --> 00:31:15,133
他的时间到了
His time is up.

590
00:31:15,306 --> 00:31:16,967
你现在打算怎样，苏菲？
What are you gonna do now, Sophie?

591
00:31:18,042 --> 00:31:19,873
我会照我说的去做
(SlGHS) I'm gonna do what I said
I was gonna do.

592
00:31:20,144 --> 00:31:22,874
做什么？杀了那个女孩？
杀了你自己吗？
What? Kill the girl?
Kill yourself?

593
00:31:23,047 --> 00:31:24,947
克劳斯不在乎那个孩子
Klaus does not care
about the child.

594
00:31:25,984 --> 00:31:27,417
我在乎
ELlJAH: I do.

595
00:31:33,825 --> 00:31:37,591
我带来了证据
我想帮你们的证据
And I bring proof
of my intent to help you.

596
00:31:39,197 --> 00:31:40,892
你们已故朋友的尸体
The body of your fallen friend,

597
00:31:41,065 --> 00:31:43,863
我从马赛尔那里要来的
which I procured
from Marcel himself.

598
00:31:44,869 --> 00:31:46,359
简安
Jane-Anne?

599
00:31:47,438 --> 00:31:49,167
愿她安息
May she be granted peace.

600
00:31:53,511 --> 00:31:55,069
克劳斯会答应你的条件
Klaus will agree to your terms.

601
00:31:56,147 --> 00:31:57,409
我还需要一点时间
I just need a little more time.

602
00:31:57,582 --> 00:31:59,379
给过你时间了，时间已过
You had your time.
It's passed.

603
00:31:59,550 --> 00:32:01,040
闭嘴
爱格妮丝
Shut up, Agnes.

604
00:32:03,922 --> 00:32:06,254
先接受交易吧
眼下
For now,
accept the deal.

605
00:32:06,925 --> 00:32:09,086
那个女孩和孩子要安然无恙
The girl and the child
remain unharmed...

606
00:32:11,062 --> 00:32:12,962
否则克劳斯会把你们全杀光
...or Klaus
will kill you all.

607
00:32:19,437 --> 00:32:21,132
我也会帮他
And I will help him.

608
00:32:35,853 --> 00:32:38,720
难道我没说清楚我想一个人静一静吗？
Have I not made clear
my desire to be left alone?

609
00:32:39,023 --> 00:32:40,047
每十年你至少会有一次
Well, you demand
to be left alone

610
00:32:40,224 --> 00:32:41,521
要求一个人静一静
at least once a decade.

611
00:32:41,693 --> 00:32:43,354
你的话已经不再有影响力了
Your words have ceased
to have impact.

612
00:32:44,495 --> 00:32:47,020
你为什么一直叨念着那个孩子？
Why must you keep harping on
about the baby?

613
00:32:47,231 --> 00:32:49,131
那个孩子绝对不会被生出来
That child will never be born.

614
00:32:49,334 --> 00:32:52,770
事实上，海莉现在很可能已经死了
In fact, Hayley is
probably dead already.

615
00:32:54,339 --> 00:32:56,534
你绝对不能就这样离开
You will not walk away from this.

616
00:32:57,308 --> 00:32:59,173
放开我
Let me go.

617
00:32:59,978 --> 00:33:01,206
休想
I will not!

618
00:33:05,683 --> 00:33:07,048
别逼我再说一次
Don't make me say it again.

619
00:33:07,218 --> 00:33:10,119
我不会放开你的，我绝对不会
I will not let go.
I will never let go.

620
00:33:14,692 --> 00:33:15,989
即使我永世都得
Even if I have to spend eternity

621
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:18,651
拯救你，让你摆脱固执、任性
saving you from your own
stubborn, petulant, 

622
00:33:18,830 --> 00:33:20,422
卑鄙的自己
vile self.

623
00:33:22,934 --> 00:33:24,196
如果我必须像父亲过去那样殴打你
If I have to beat you as
father used to beat you

624
00:33:24,369 --> 00:33:25,893
来提醒你你的人性
to remind you
of your own humanity.

625
00:33:26,904 --> 00:33:28,667
提醒你去关心一切
To care about anything.

626
00:33:39,884 --> 00:33:42,478
你实在是太可悲了，以利亚
You're beyond pathetic, Elijah.

627
00:33:45,623 --> 00:33:47,318
谁更可悲？
Who's more pathetic?

628
00:33:49,027 --> 00:33:51,495
是那个盼望让家庭完整的人
The one who sees hope to
make his family whole...

629
00:33:54,265 --> 00:33:58,167
还是那个
只能从自己的恐惧中看世界的懦夫？
...or the coward who can only see
the world through his own fear?

630
00:33:58,336 --> 00:34:01,362
几个世纪以来，我什么都不在乎
I haven't cared about
anything for centuries.

631
00:34:01,506 --> 00:34:03,371
你到底为什么在乎？
Why on earth do you?

632
00:34:04,776 --> 00:34:06,300
因为我让你失望了
Because I failed you.

633
00:34:09,247 --> 00:34:11,841
因为第一次父亲动手打你
Because the first time
our father laid a hand on you,

634
00:34:12,016 --> 00:34:13,677
我应该直接打死他
I should've struck him dead.

635
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:17,615
我还向你保证过
And I made a promise to you.

636
00:34:20,091 --> 00:34:22,457
家庭总是
Always.
Forever.

637
00:34:23,594 --> 00:34:25,562
永远高于一切
Family above all.

638
00:34:43,748 --> 00:34:47,309
你真是个多愁善感的傻瓜
You are a sentimental fool.

639
00:34:48,219 --> 00:34:49,777
也许吧
Perhaps.

640
00:34:52,390 --> 00:34:54,756
尽管如此，我也坚持了这么久了
不是吗？
But I've lasted this long in spite of it,
haven't l?

641
00:35:14,912 --> 00:35:18,541
家庭的联系赐予了我们无尽的力量
ELlJAH: The bond of family blesses us
with an immeasurable power.

642
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:31,885
但是我们也要接受随之而来的一切
But we also
must accept what comes with it.

643
00:35:39,604 --> 00:35:43,540
它带给我们无条件
无歉意去爱的
It gives us a responsibility,
to love without condition.

644
00:35:45,943 --> 00:35:47,410
责任
Without apology.

645
00:35:58,523 --> 00:36:00,354
我们永远都不能放弃这种联系的力量
We can never waiver
from the power of that bond,

646
00:36:00,525 --> 00:36:02,584
即使受到考验
even when it is tested.

647
00:36:06,097 --> 00:36:10,227
这种联系滋春着我们
给我们力量
The bond nourishes us,
gives us strength.

648
00:36:13,137 --> 00:36:15,071
没有这力量，我们就一无所有
Without that power,
we are nothing.

649
00:36:17,275 --> 00:36:21,177
这座城市曾经是我的家
我不在的日子里
This town was my home once,
and in my absence,

650
00:36:21,345 --> 00:36:24,746
马赛尔得到了我想要的一切
Marcel has got everything
I ever wanted.

651
00:36:25,349 --> 00:36:28,079
权力，忠诚
Power.
Loyalty.

652
00:36:29,854 --> 00:36:31,481
家庭
Family.

653
00:36:32,089 --> 00:36:35,422
我按自己样子塑造他，他却青出于蓝
I made him in my image,
and he has bettered me.

654
00:36:38,362 --> 00:36:40,455
我要他的一切
I want what he has.

655
00:36:41,899 --> 00:36:43,423
我要夺回来
I want it back.

656
00:36:45,269 --> 00:36:46,793
我要成为王
I want to be king.

657
00:36:52,210 --> 00:36:54,508
所以这孩子对你来说
ELlJAH: So, is that all
this child means to you?

658
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:57,575
只是夺权的工具？
A grab for power?

659
00:36:59,483 --> 00:37:01,178
那对你来说意味着什么呢？
What does it mean to you?

660
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:04,285
我觉得…
I think...

661
00:37:04,755 --> 00:37:06,950
这个孩子能够给你你一直以为
...this child could offer you
the one thing

662
00:37:06,991 --> 00:37:08,788
你得不到的东西
that you've never
believed you had.

663
00:37:09,193 --> 00:37:10,820
是什么？
And what's that?

664
00:37:13,297 --> 00:37:15,288
家庭无条件的爱
The unconditional
love of family.

665
00:37:23,407 --> 00:37:25,807
告诉苏菲德弗罗，我们成交了
Tell Sophie Deveraux
we have a deal.

666
00:37:40,524 --> 00:37:41,821
你还好吧？
You all right?

667
00:37:42,026 --> 00:37:43,516
只是吸入了灰尘
Just dust.

668
00:37:43,961 --> 00:37:45,690
这地方真古老
This place is ancient.

669
00:37:46,063 --> 00:37:47,860
是的，但这里应该够我们用了
Yes.
It should serve our purposes.

670
00:37:49,967 --> 00:37:53,164
这是我们在法语区的庇护所
It's a sanctuary from
our business in the Quarter.

671
00:37:55,339 --> 00:37:58,001
现在你是这个家中最重要的人
Right now, you're the most
important person in this family.

672
00:37:58,175 --> 00:37:59,642
你需要一个安定的家
You need a good home.

673
00:38:02,713 --> 00:38:04,180
我很好奇
So, I'm curious.

674
00:38:04,915 --> 00:38:07,679
在这段时间里
有没有人间过你的感受？
In all this time, has anyone
asked you how you feel?

675
00:38:07,885 --> 00:38:09,113
和一个疯子一夜情之后
About having a miracle baby

676
00:38:09,287 --> 00:38:11,152
怀上一个奇迹般孩子的感受吗？
with a psychotic one-night stand?

677
00:38:11,856 --> 00:38:13,153
身为一个母亲的感受
About being a mother.

678
00:38:21,098 --> 00:38:22,588
我…
I....

679
00:38:23,768 --> 00:38:26,100
我一出生就被遗弃了
I was abandoned when I was born,

680
00:38:26,270 --> 00:38:28,830
我一变成狼，我的畚父母
and my adoptive parents
kicked me out

681
00:38:29,006 --> 00:38:31,133
就把我赶了出去
the second that I turned into a wolf.

682
00:38:32,843 --> 00:38:37,542
所以我真的不太知道
做母亲的感受
So, I don't really know how I feel
about being a mother

683
00:38:37,715 --> 00:38:41,776
因为我从来就没有过好母亲
because I never
really had a good one.

684
00:38:43,954 --> 00:38:45,785
我会一直保护你
I will always protect you.

685
00:38:48,359 --> 00:38:49,883
我向你保证
You have my word on that.

686
00:38:52,997 --> 00:38:55,625
高尚的以利亚向来信守承诺
And noble Elijah
always keeps his word.

687
00:38:56,000 --> 00:38:56,989
搞定了吗？
Is it done?

688
00:38:57,168 --> 00:38:58,931
事实上，搞定了
As a matter of fact, yes.

689
00:38:59,270 --> 00:39:01,397
你见不得人的交易非常顺利
Your underhanded deal
worked quite well.

690
00:39:01,872 --> 00:39:04,534
马赛尔非常高兴地接受了我的血
Marcel was only too happy
to accept my blood,

691
00:39:04,742 --> 00:39:07,404
正如他接受了我由衷的道歉
even as he accepted
my heartfelt apologies.

692
00:39:07,578 --> 00:39:09,341
他的手下提艾里还活着
His man Thierry yet lives

693
00:39:09,513 --> 00:39:12,414
我依旧是法语区受欢迎的客人
and I remain a welcome guest
in the French Quarter.

694
00:39:12,583 --> 00:39:15,177
我现在担心的
My only concern now

695
00:39:15,353 --> 00:39:18,015
是那群无耻的女巫
is this coven
of impudent witches.

696
00:39:18,189 --> 00:39:20,020
我相信她们是可敬的
I believe them to be honorable.

697
00:39:20,524 --> 00:39:22,389
她们确实放了海莉
They did release Hayley to me.

698
00:39:23,160 --> 00:39:25,924
尽管她们还没有完全坦白
Although they haven't been
entirely forthcoming.

699
00:39:26,330 --> 00:39:29,527
马赛尔显然有什么她们需要的东西
Marcel obviously has something
that they need.

700
00:39:30,334 --> 00:39:31,858
她们不想他死
They don't want him dead.

701
00:39:32,636 --> 00:39:34,331
一定有原因
There must be a reason why.

702
00:39:51,389 --> 00:39:53,414
我想外面风平浪静了？
I assume it's all quiet out there?

703
00:39:55,459 --> 00:39:57,927
女巫们识相的话就不会使用魔法
The witches know better
than to use magic.

704
00:39:58,763 --> 00:40:00,890
她们知道一旦施魔法我能感受到
They know I can sense it
when they do.

705
00:40:04,602 --> 00:40:06,001
那些老家伙呢？
What about the old ones?

706
00:40:06,670 --> 00:40:08,729
他们很危险
我不想他们伤害你
They're dangerous,
and I don't want them to hurt you.

707
00:40:08,906 --> 00:40:10,430
真祖吗？
The Originals?

708
00:40:11,709 --> 00:40:14,576
黛维娜，强大如你
Davina, as powerful as you are?

709
00:40:14,745 --> 00:40:16,542
他们毫无机会的
They don't stand
a chance.

710
00:40:18,048 --> 00:40:19,242
除了他用来
ELlJAH: In addition
to the secret weapon

711
00:40:19,417 --> 00:40:20,611
控制女巫的秘密武器
he uses to control the witches,

712
00:40:20,785 --> 00:40:23,913
马赛尔组建了一支小型的吸血鬼部队
Marcel has assembled
a small army of vampires.

713
00:40:25,022 --> 00:40:28,458
齐心协力，我们可以从内部摧毁他们
Working together,
we could destroy them from the inside.

714
00:40:28,759 --> 00:40:29,783
蕾贝卡呢？
And what of Rebekah?

715
00:40:29,960 --> 00:40:31,552
她公主性子耍完没有
Has she stopped her
pouting long enough

716
00:40:31,729 --> 00:40:33,026
要不要一起来找乐子呢？
to join the fun?

717
00:40:34,698 --> 00:40:37,394
她已经明显表达了没兴趣
She has made her
disinterest quite clear.

718
00:40:37,668 --> 00:40:38,930
我想是被插了太多次匕首
One too many times daggered

719
00:40:39,103 --> 00:40:40,764
被关了太多次棺材了
and shoved in a box, I gather?

720
00:40:41,005 --> 00:40:44,839
也或许她不赞同
Or, perhaps, she doesn't share

721
00:40:45,009 --> 00:40:48,570
你坚定地认为我可以被拯牧的信念
your unwavering belief
that I can be saved.

722
00:40:48,979 --> 00:40:50,640
蕾贝卡也许会给我们惊喜
Rebekah may surprise us yet.

723
00:40:51,615 --> 00:40:53,845
毕竟我们都许下了同样的誓官
After all, we all
swore the same vow.

724
00:40:56,287 --> 00:40:59,347
我希望她待得远远的
I hope she stays far away.

725
00:41:00,991 --> 00:41:03,960
因为我想要收回这座城市
Because in my desire
to reclaim this town,

726
00:41:04,128 --> 00:41:07,359
想要从马赛尔手中偷回他最珍视的东西
to steal from Marcel that which
he holds most dear,

727
00:41:08,032 --> 00:41:12,093
我意识到最重要的一个弱点
I have realized one massive
vulnerability.

728
00:41:13,471 --> 00:41:16,702
马赛尔最可能利用的一个弱点
One weakness that
Marcel could exploit.

729
00:41:17,041 --> 00:41:18,633
是什么？
And what is that?

730
00:41:20,344 --> 00:41:21,333
你
You.

731
00:41:25,716 --> 00:41:27,946
原谅我，我的哥哥
Forgive me, my brother.

732
00:41:29,720 --> 00:41:31,654
爱里没有权力
There is no power in love.

733
00:41:32,857 --> 00:41:35,018
仁慈让你软弱
Mercy makes you weak.

734
00:41:35,426 --> 00:41:39,260
家人让你软弱
Family makes you weak.

735
00:41:41,799 --> 00:41:43,960
我要想赢得这场战争
If I'm going to win this war...

736
00:41:45,336 --> 00:41:46,963
我必须孤身奋战
...I have to do it alone.

737
00:41:52,076 --> 00:41:56,342
片名：创始吸血鬼（第一季）

